Package: chessvision
Title: Computational Chess Performance Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Rakkshet", "Singhaal", 
           email = "rakkshet.singhaal@kellogg.northwestern.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R interface to the chessvision-py Python library for 
    computational chess performance analysis. Transforms PGN game archives 
    into tidy datasets and applies machine learning models to profile 
    playing style, classify error archetypes, forecast ELO trajectories, 
    and generate causally grounded training recommendations.
